Design a modern Job Analytics Dashboard using a clean, professional layout with a card-based interface. Use the following color scheme and design elements:

Color Palette:
	•	Background (Dark Theme): #121212
	•	Card Background: #1E1E1E
	•	Primary Text: #FFFFFF
	•	Secondary Text: #B0B0B0
	•	Button (Primary): #6C63FF
	•	Button Text: #FFFFFF
	•	Success Tag: #28C76F
	•	Failure Tag: #EA5455
	•	Chart Success: #28C76F
	•	Chart Failure: #EA5455

Typography:
	•	Font: Inter or Roboto
	•	Font Weight: 400 (normal), 600 (headings)
	•	Title Size: 24px
	•	Label Size: 14px
	•	Value Text: 16px

Layout & Components:
	1.	Top Header (Sticky)
	•	Text: “Job Analytics Dashboard”
	•	Font size: 24px, bold, white text on dark background
	2.	Filter Panel (Card - Left Section)
	•	Background: #1E1E1E with rounded corners (8px) and shadow
	•	Elements:
	•	Quick Filters: Buttons for “Today”, “7 Days”, “30 Days” (#6C63FF)
	•	Custom Date Range: Calendar pickers with subtle borders
	•	Apply Button: Filled with #6C63FF, white text
	•	Reset Filters: Text button in #B0B0B0
	3.	Job Status Overview (Card - Below Filters)
	•	Donut Chart
	•	Success: #28C76F, Failure: #EA5455
	•	Center label showing count: “Success: X | Failure: Y”
	4.	Job Details Panel (Card - Right Section)
	•	Background: #1E1E1E, rounded corners, subtle shadow
	•	Table-style layout with the following columns:
	•	Job Name: White bold text
	•	Status: Colored pill tags:
	•	Green (#28C76F) for Success
	•	Red (#EA5455) for Failure
	•	Execution Time: Light gray text (#B0B0B0)
	•	Log Path: Truncated with tooltip on hover
	•	Add subtle hover effect on rows: background #2A2A2A